title: Are Influencers Stupid With Their Money?
description:
It's no secret that influencers are FOOLISHLY loaded these days with all their brand deals and crazy investments, but the real question is... where does it all go? Today we talk about the crazy cash flow we've witnessed from these internet stars, and confess to our own wild spending habits.
